### Objective
#### This project will analyize and and conduct hypothesis testing on the tooth growth R data package.  The data specifically documentstThe Effect of Vitamin C on Tooth Growth in Guinea Pigs and is found at https://stat.ethz.ch/R-manual/R-devel/library/datasets/html/ToothGrowth.html


```{r, echo=FALSE}
# Preliminarty config

attach(ToothGrowth)

doses <- unique(ToothGrowth$dose)
meanLength <- aggregate(ToothGrowth$len , list(ToothGrowth$dose) , mean)
colnames(meanLength) <- c('dose' , 'mean_length')



```

```{r}


